{"_id":"P2oup74n6LQlJ49K","name":"[6] Yeoman (MF) (Weryn of Clan Ailt)","content":"<p>Weryn is in a difficult position. As head of Clan Ailt, he is responsible for all of the members of his clan, but he is also a yeoman who must serve the bailiff. Frequently these two duties have clashed and he has been forced to oppress his own clansmen. He has tried to make up for it by sharing out the food he can spare after feeding his wife, sister and two parents, but it has done little to mend the mistrust caused when, under the swords of the two mercenaries, he was forced to beat his own cousin, Ailarn (@Compendium[hm-loc-charmic.journals.y3xOdo1SN5UGU0Kw]{[13] Cottar (Ailarn of Clan Heryla)}), unconscious for stealing food.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"PusKspNsRtwjEZQs":3},"flags":{"entityorder":{"order":1200000},"cf":{"id":"temp_vp55g1baur9","color":"#000000"}}}
{"_id":"QEBt3v8AoBHcIgVa","name":"[35] Villein (Narus of Clan Drebor)","content":"<p>Narus is the younger brother of Mabisi (@Compendium[hm-loc-charmic.journals.XgtMIO05JAhEXG90]{[23] Villein (Mabisi of Clan Drebor)}). Also fairly successful, he has come through the hard times with his sense of humour intact. Even in the hardest times, he would be cracking jokes and raising a weary smile from the other men. He lives with his wife and three distant cousins (orphans). He and his wife can’t have children, so they have adopted children from within the clan who have lost their parents.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"PusKspNsRtwjEZQs":3},"flags":{"entityorder":{"order":7000000},"cf":{"id":"temp_vp55g1baur9","color":"#000000"}}}
{"_id":"RGrnBjT8Z2QJqLM4","name":"[E] Meadowland","content":"<h2>Meadowland</h2><p>This is the best land on the manor and is reserved for hay to feed the livestock over the winter.</p>\n","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"PusKspNsRtwjEZQs":3},"flags":{"entityorder":{"order":1000000},"cf":{"id":"temp_7b68j8e8k4","color":"#000000"}}}
{"_id":"RSN7rtLkuOSwlRp1","name":"[16] Cottar (Eadil of Clan Heryla)","content":"<p>Eadil and his wife would not have survived without the support of the Clan Head, Tokra (@Compendium[hm-loc-charmic.journals.Ri7HcOMfc1x9PGbJ]{[9] Villein (Tokra of Clan Heryla)}). He made sure Eadil was able to slip away from work parties to hunt rabbits with his sling. That bit of extra protein has kept them alive, though his wife’s joints are swollen and she can hardly walk.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"PusKspNsRtwjEZQs":3},"flags":{"entityorder":{"order":3200000},"cf":{"id":"temp_vp55g1baur9","color":"#000000"}}}
{"_id":"Ri7HcOMfc1x9PGbJ","name":"[9] Villein (Tokra of Clan Heryla)","content":"<p>A member of the largest clan in the village, Tokra’s family has survived by putting the clan’s interests ahead of the village’s interests. A strong man, Tokra’s brother Arrel proved to be very good with the crosscut saw. He worked hard and didn’t complain, leading Lynd the timberwright to make him foreman in charge of assigning duties. He made sure that Clan Heryla got the best duties, with the most time for scavenging in the forest and working their plots, at the expense of the other clans. Despite the unpopularity that caused, the two brothers were able to support their wives, two unmarried sisters and Tokra’s four teenage children. Arrel’s children, who were younger, died anyway.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"PusKspNsRtwjEZQs":3},"flags":{"entityorder":{"order":1800000},"cf":{"id":"temp_vp55g1baur9","color":"#000000"}}}
{"_id":"RzpiC1PvOmSJdO6j","name":"[30] Half-Villein (Anrorian of Clan Drebor)","content":"<p>Anrorian and his family could not have survived the last five years without the generous support of their clan head, Mabisi (@Compendium[hm-loc-charmic.journals.XgtMIO05JAhEXG90]{[23] Villein (Mabisi of Clan Drebor)}). In return, Anrorian has pledged his unconditional loyalty to him. Anrorian lives with his wife, adult son, his son’s wife, teenage daughter and elderly aunt and uncle.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"PusKspNsRtwjEZQs":3},"flags":{"entityorder":{"order":6000000},"cf":{"id":"temp_vp55g1baur9","color":"#000000"}}}
